task.summary: Default task
Update OpdsUriResponder to ensure that the absolute self link is serialized, which is required for peer to peer transfers.
Update cache and NanoLrs version
Bump version
Handle going to base point view with no arguments e.g. after logout, up navigation when the parent activity is not in the back stack.
Update misc.xml
Use sourceSets to add assets from core to Android module instead of copying
Update Dari and Pashto registratoin form
Update build files towards being able to use proguard.
Improve UMUtil passXmlThrough methods for use modifying HTML served for epubs etc.
Work in Progress: implementation of epub pagination
Fix issue handling OPDS xhtml content caused by passXmlThrough refactor
Pagination work in progress: start of adding support for pagination within a single xhtml document.
Initial implementation of EpubWebView that paginates a single HTML file
Update EpubWebView to disable vertical scrolling
Add activity_id to xapi package url query parameters.
Introduce async http and overhaul epub container view
Update to Android plugin for Gradle 3.0.0
Add improved table of contents for EPUB. Provides a hierarchical table of contents support for the navigation drawer on the side of the EPUB. Shows the cover image and author name.
Add new Catalog Entry View mode suitable for standard OPDS catalogs that have thumbnails for entries but do not have a banner image.
Add maven publishing for app-javase
Handle resovleLink when the base href has no folder structure and href is a relative link.
Bump version

Improve OPDS scanning support and refine epub pagination:
1. OPDS Directory scanning support methods improved to handle multiple authors, pickup content language, and handle cover images. 2. EPUB pagination correctly limited the maximum height of images (to avoid them being split up between columns). 3. EPUB viewer script will automatically convert vh units to pixels to workaround a bug in which vh units are calculated as zero (affected African Storybook Project EPUBs).
Implement AppBarLayout on Android for the base point activity. Start implementation of filtering interface options.
Refactor threading out of core in preparation for GWT.
Refactor Threads out of core for GWT. Add new, improved, async HttpCache.
Remove / refactor out of the way references to SQLException, Calendar, WeakReference, FileNotFoundException for GWT implementation

Connect OPDS feed load with HTTP caching, improve http caching, improve image loading
1. OPDS feeds now load via the cache 2. Http caching responses indicate if the response is considered fresh or stale 3. ImageLoader will make a second http request only if needed, and update an already set image only if the network response indicates the underlying data has changed. 4. Resolves CatalogPresenter memory leak
Use SQL database for management of http cache db to improve http cache scalability and performance.
Implement testing for HttpCache, handle edge cases around entry validation.
Refactor OPDS entry and feed to using getters/setters instead of variable access.
Update tests to handle refactored OPDS classes

Merge branch 'p2p2' of github.com:UstadMobile/UstadMobile into p2p2
Update issues with moving from using a String[] array for OPDS links to using UmOpdsLink.
# Conflicts: # core/src/main/java/com/ustadmobile/core/impl/UstadMobileSystemImpl.java
Fix display of cover image using UmOpdsLink instead of String array
Add SCORM manifest processing.
Update Scorm View and remove usages of newInstance in core (to avoid GWT issues)
Remove core usage of getClass.getResourceAsStream to avoid GWT issues.
Update activity epub pager to avoid usage as library issues. Publish lib-core-fs library.
Publish lib-core-fs-jcommon
Bump version number
Fix lib-core-fs-jcommon artifact name typo
Add new persistence layer, upgrade to using Java 1.8
Small updates to handling opds persistence.
Update to enable the base content directory name to be set using appconfig.properties
Update to enable the base content directory name to be set using appconfig.properties

Update to avoid layout merging issues when app is used as a library.
Issues appear to have been triggered by xmlns:tools usage in layout resource files
Switch to using a dedicated android library maven publish plugin.
Update acquisition task handling of notification channel, use of Opds feed links.
Basic implementation of CatalogView where entries are loaded to/from SQLite.
